CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 9, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "Dainty -  Loraine Taylor of Philly made a dainty and fetching model at the Hotel Roosevelt at the Beauty Shop Owners style show.  The flattering parasol is on its way back into style, or didn't you know?"
TitMainTitle: Loraine Taylor wearing hat and holding large parasol at Beauty Shop Owner's fashion show, Roosevelt Hotel
